LibRRD
======

To build the GUI, run `sbt deploy`.  Generated files are added to `gui/`.
To build the CLI, run `npm install` (this requires Node.js v20 and npm).

To run the CLI: `node cli/cli.js [args…]`
To run the GUI: launch a webserver in `gui/` and open `index.html` in your browser (e.g. run `python3 -m http.server` and browse to `http://localhost:8000`).